transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling customer service, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, my name is Phil Glover and I'm trying to change my shipment.

Speaker 1: I would like to go ahead and cancel until I further notify you to reapply the account again.

Speaker 2: Okay, let me pull your account up. What's your name and birthday?

Speaker 1: 12-3-57, Phil Glover.

Speaker 2: Thank you, one second.

Speaker 1: Looks like you already did it. You don't have an active prescription with us.

Speaker 2: Okay, that's a few questions that I do have.

Speaker 1: What I did last time is I did deal of the month and that's what I'm listed at now.

Speaker 2: Will that be the way I respond to you?

Speaker 1: In other words, until I do another deal of the month, you won't charge my credit card and send anything to me.

Speaker 2: That's great. Thanks for your help.

Speaker 1: You're welcome. Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye.
